She is a amazing doctor. I visited her for my wife . She was having abdominal on and off Pain issue for very long. I took her to many doctors before but got no relief. Then came to know Dr. Hamra. She was spot on with diagnosis and prescribed some tests and medication and my wife was better in 5 days. 
The doctor is kind and generous. I recommend her strongly. May God bless her so that she can bless all her patients with her skills.

My wife and me visited the doctor for normal checkup during 1st month of pregnancy. though waiting time was almost 1 hour and poor reception facilities, finally got a chance to meet the doctor, she is very genuine, warm, friendly and motherly like lady. my wife was very nervous but the moment she entered in the doctor room she got relax because the way doctor greeted us and was able to discuss everything she was experiencing,  she listened very carefully and advised some exercise and diet plan and some test which happen at the same time . I would strongly recommend the doctor.
